# Client Brief

## Client

Working Name: TBD Lifestyle Company

## Industry

Lifestyle products manufacturing and retail.

## Business Overview

The company manufactures selected lifestyle products while sourcing additional products from strategic suppliers. Products are sold through retail stores, e-commerce, and wholesale partners.

The company has experienced rapid growth over the past few years, resulting in fragmented reporting processes across departments.

## Current Challenges

- Reporting is largely manual.
- Data exists in multiple spreadsheets and systems.
- KPIs are inconsistently defined across departments.
- Executives spend excessive time validating reports.
- Analysts spend more time preparing data than generating insights.

## Engagement Goal

Design and implement a scalable analytics foundation that provides reliable, automated reporting and enables future analytical capabilities across the organization.